title: Quit Arguing for Your Failures

description:

Do you argue with people about how you aren’t good enough?
 
Example: "Hey husband. Do you think I can lose weight?"
He says yes. You say "BUT" ..that’s a sure sign you won’t lose weight.
 
Today I’m helping you see this easy roadblock you can remove.
